    dc:description "FIGURES 37–43. Genitalia of Plutodes spp. 37–39, P. nilgirica, male, Munnar: 37, ventral view, 38, valva, 39, aedeagus (vesica not everted); 40–41, P. subcaudata, male, Rishop: 40, ventral view, 41, aedeagus; 42, ditto, female, Ravangla; 43, P. exquisita, female, Singtam (corpus bursae torn). (diagnostic characters indicated by black lines)." ;
